data.text:
July 3, 2024

Instead of being honest with the voters, Don Davis once again is falling in line behind his Democrat party bosses by “declin[ing] to say whether Biden should remain in the race.”

Davis is a known Biden supporter. He just hosted Biden in the district last summer.
